id: pmc-84ow
title: Merge release metadata before npm publication
description: "Daily Release run 29274764877 published pm-changelog@2026.7.13 and then failed because its direct HEAD:main push was rejected by protected-branch policy. Replace the direct push with a release-branch pull-request transaction that merges validated metadata before any irreversible npm publication."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[5]: branch-protection,github-actions,production-readiness,release,transaction-safety
created_at: "2026-07-14T00:04:12.052Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-14T01:23:54.359Z"
deadline: "2026-07-16T00:04:12.052Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-14T00:13:32.226Z"
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: "Workflow requests pull-requests:write and never directly pushes HEAD:main; release metadata is pushed to a deterministic branch and merged via a PR before npm publish; merged main is verified at the intended npm version; tag is created on the merged commit only after publish succeeds; retry paths reuse an existing PR/version and skip already-published npm versions; workflow syntax, full release gate, and TypeScript workflow-contract tests pass."
definition_of_ready: Failure reproduced from GitHub logs; branch protection confirmed; npm and tag state inspected; no duplicate pm item found.
value: "Restores trustworthy, recoverable daily releases without weakening main protection."
impact: Prevents npm/GitHub split-brain releases across all future pm-changelog versions.
outcome: Daily Release works with protected main using only free GitHub features and the repository GITHUB_TOKEN.
why_now: The latest manual Daily Release failed after publication and the workflow remains broken for every future change.
parent: pmc-yy8d
reviewer: codex-root
risk: critical
confidence: high
release: v2026.7.14
severity: critical
environment: GitHub Actions Daily Release run 29274764877 on protected main
repro_steps: "Dispatch Daily Release from main with changes since the latest tag; observe npm publish succeed and git push origin HEAD:main fail with GH006."
resolution: Protected-branch-compatible release PR transaction implemented and verified.
expected_result: Release metadata reaches protected main before registry publication.
actual_result: "Direct main push removed; exact-SHA PR merge, merged-main release gate, idempotent publish, and exact-commit tag are enforced by workflow and TypeScript tests."
affected_version: 2026.7.13
fixed_version: 2026.7.14
component: release-automation
regression: false
customer_impact: "Automated releases can publish artifacts that are not represented by main, a release tag, or GitHub release notes."
