close_reason: Implementation and all local acceptance gates complete; live workflow dispatch follows reviewed merge and will reopen on any production discrepancy.
body: "The release workflow currently publishes npm before trying to persist its version and changelog commit. Protected main rejects that direct push, so npm can advance while GitHub main/tag/release remain incomplete. The workflow must create or reuse a deterministic release PR, merge it through normal branch protection, verify the merged version, then publish and tag the exact merged commit. Retries must recover cleanly from partial runs without choosing a new version or duplicating publication."
